{
  "stem": "24515.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And one uncle, who I think never was bigger than 5'3' in his life, faced a Nazi in full uniform.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He wanted the apartment.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my uncle told him to go and [? drown ?] himself and bringing him documents or else no.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the man left.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I think, I seem to remember, that my uncles, in the end, did not stay in the apartment.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Where they went, I do not know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I knew next day, from the news and from the-- from the rumor mill, the-- you know, the grapevine, that many shops had been destroyed and many synagogues have been destroyed and so on, you see?",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, I didn't know this at the time, but the-- my father was one of the very first men in Chemnitz to be taken.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he was taken by the Chemnitz police, who put him into a prison cell.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we are pretty sure, in our own minds, that they did this in order to save him, to take him out of the hands of the Nazi gangs.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because three times during the day, the proper Nazi gangs, with their, you know, uniforms on, showed up and demanded him.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And went away when they found he wasn't there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I'm convinced he wouldn't have lived to the street corner if they had got him.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The police held him as long as they could, apparently.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then he went to-- was sent to Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that would be the early morning of the 10th, I suppose.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "See, because we called Kristallnacht 9th through the 10th, you see?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, in the end, even my mother had to tell me that father was in a concentration camp, and he was in Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
